  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Inclusion criteria for myomectomy as; abnormal uterine, pressure related symptoms,
             infertility and recurrent pregnancy loss in patients between 18 and 45 years old

          2. Single myoma.

          3. Women with BMI between 18.5-29.9 kg/m2.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Pregnancy.

          2. Patients with bleeding tendency

          3. Previous laparotomies.

          4. Patients with concomitant pelvic pathologies, such as ovarian cysts.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
